Title: Personal Reflection: Proof of Growth
Date: 2026-06-20
Source: mira_020_personal_reflection.pdf
Demo Persona: Mira Vale
Privacy Level: private

I felt a brief wave of self-doubt today, thinking I haven't grown as an artist. I pulled out my sketchbooks from two years ago and compared them to my current canvases. The difference in composition control and color harmony was clear. The evidence is solid: my practice has led to real improvement.